ZH: 我喜欢吃所有的水果，除了榴莲以外。
EN: I like to eat all fruits except for durian.

ZH: 外面下了大雨，我除了带伞以外什么都没有带。
EN: It was raining heavily outside, and I didn't bring anything except an umbrella.

ZH: 这件衣服的颜色除了黑色以外，还有红色和蓝色。
EN: This clothing is available in colors other than black, such as red and blue.

ZH: 昨天我去了图书馆，除了借书以外，还做了一些研究。
EN: I went to the library yesterday, and besides borrowing books, I also did some research.

ZH: 除了旅行以外，我还喜欢骑自行车。
EN: Apart from traveling, I also enjoy riding bicycles.

ZH: 这个国家以外，我还去过其他很多地方。
EN: Besides this country, I have also been to many other places.

ZH: 除了英语以外，我也会说一点法语。
EN: Apart from English, I can also speak a little French.

ZH: 在这家餐厅除了牛肉以外，还有很多其他菜品可选择。
EN: Apart from beef, this restaurant also offers a wide variety of other dishes to choose from.

ZH: 我打算买一部新手机，但除了预算以外，还需要考虑其他因素。
EN: I plan to buy a new phone, but besides the budget, there are other factors to consider.

ZH: 除了理解问题以外，解决问题也是非常重要的。
EN: Besides understanding the problem, it is also important to solve it.

ZH: 除了关心自己，还要关心他人。
EN: Apart from caring for oneself, one should also care for others.

ZH: 除了工作以外，我还会参加一些志愿者活动。
EN: Besides work, I also participate in volunteer activities.

ZH: 除了读书以外，我也喜欢听音乐。
EN: Besides reading books, I also enjoy listening to music.

ZH: 这个游戏很好玩，除了需要智力以外，还需要一定的技巧。
EN: This game is fun; besides intelligence, it also requires some skills.

ZH: 除了认真学习以外，还需要保持身体健康。
EN: Besides studying diligently, it is also important to maintain good physical health.

ZH: 除了家人以外，朋友也是非常重要的。
EN: Besides family, friends are also very important.

ZH: 除了学习以外，我还喜欢看电影和旅行。
EN: Besides studying, I also enjoy watching movies and traveling.

ZH: 除了丰富经验以外，这份工作还需要很强的沟通能力。
EN: Apart from rich experience, this job also requires strong communication skills.

ZH: 除了中国菜以外，我也喜欢尝试其他国家的美食。
EN: Besides Chinese cuisine, I also enjoy trying food from other countries.

ZH: 除了喝水以外，还可以喝果汁和咖啡。
EN: Apart from drinking water, you can also drink fruit juice and coffee.
